Register a database: write its dbs/<db>.toml registry file

Usage: sleet register [OPTIONS] <ROOT> <DB>

Arguments:
  <ROOT>
          Fleet root URL, e.g. s3://ops/sleet/

  <DB>
          Database URL, e.g. s3://bucket/db

Options:
      --format <FORMAT>
          Output format

          Possible values:
          - text: Human-readable text
          - json: JSON matching the subcommand's response schema
          
          [default: text]

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')
